---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="关于我 - Overthinker">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-24 w-full">
    <div class="mb-12 border-b border-bg-surface pb-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">关于我</h1>
      <p class="text-text-muted text-lg">过度思考者，代码雕刻师</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-p:text-text-muted prose-headings:text-white max-w-none">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-start mb-12">
        <div class="w-full md:w-1/3">
          <div class="aspect-square rounded-2xl overflow-hidden bg-bg-surface border border-bg-surface-hover flex items-center justify-center relative group">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary-500/20 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity z-10"></div>
            <!-- Placeholder avatar -->
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="64" height="64" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-primary-400"><path d="M18 20a6 6 0 0 0-12 0"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="4"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/></svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="w-full md:w-2/3">
          <h3>🌟 简单自我介绍一下</h3>
          <p>你好！我是 <strong>Overthinker</strong>。</p>
          <p>我是一个在大学的海洋中挣扎求生的过度思考者，正在将屎山雕琢成艺术品的路上...</p>
          <p>我的技术栈主要集中在前端领域，特别是 Vue 和 Astro。我喜欢造轮子，也喜欢分享我学到的新知识。在这个博客里，你可以看到我的学习笔记、我的生活日常，以及我自己封装的一些 Vue 组件。</p>
          
          <h3 class="mt-8">🚀 技能栈</h3>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-4">
            {['Vue', 'Astro', 'TypeScript', 'Tailwind CSS', 'GSAP', 'C++', 'Node.js'].map(skill => (
              <span class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-bg-surface border border-bg-surface-hover rounded-md text-sm font-medium hover:border-primary-500/50 transition-colors cursor-default">
                {skill}
              </span>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-bg-surface/50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-bg-surface mt-12">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 mt-0">联系我</h3>
        <p class="mb-6">如果你对我的开源项目感兴趣，或者想和我交流技术，欢迎通过以下方式联系我：</p>
        
        <ul class="list-none pl-0 space-y-4">
          <li>
            <a href="https://github.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex items-center gap-3 text-text-base hover:text-primary-400 transition-colors no-underline">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M15 22v-4a4.8 4.8 0 0 0-1-3.5c3 0 6-2 6-5.5.08-1.25-.27-2.48-1-3.5.28-1.15.28-2.35 0-3.5 0 0-1 0-3 1.5-2.64-.5-5.36-.5-8 0C6 2 5 2 5 2c-.3 1.15-.3 2.35 0 3.5A5.403 5.403 0 0 0 4 9c0 3.5 3 5.5 6 5.5-.39.49-.68 1.05-.85 1.65-.17.6-.22 1.23-.15 1.85v4"/><path d="M9 18c-4.51 2-5-2-7-2"/></svg>
              <span>GitHub</span>
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="mailto:hello@example.com" class="flex items-center gap-3 text-text-base hover:text-primary-400 transition-colors no-underline">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect width="20" height="16" x="2" y="4" rx="2"/><path d="m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7"/></svg>
              <span>Email: hello@example.com</span>
            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
